title: DEBUG!
new-page: true
is-card: true
tags: debug_card
view-if: debug
on-arrival: month_actions += 1
card-image: img/achievements/perrosanxe.png
go-to: debug_menu


@debug_menu
new-page: true

= DEBUG CARD!

You should not be seeing this in a normal game. Please report a bug!

