@psoe_inject_sanchez_1
title: Set leader: Pedro Sánchez (pre-barones coup)
on-arrival: psoe_barons_revolted = false
call: bye_rubalcaba.sanchez

Set Pedro Sánchez as PSOE leader (pre-barones coup).

- @inject_party: Back
- @post_event: Done

