@psc_congreso_split_inject
title: Split PSC from PSOE in the congreso
choose-if: not psc_split
unavailable-subtitle: PSC is already split from the PSOE
call: psc_congreso_split

Split PSC from the PSOE in the congreso elections.

- @inject_party: Back
- @post_event: Done

@ciu_inject
title: CiU (and evolutions)

** CiU situations **

- @inject_party: Back
- @cdc_unio_inject
- @dl_inject
- @pdcat_inject
- @post_event: Done

@cdc_unio_inject
title: Split UDC, create CDC
choose-if: not unio_split
unavailable-subtitle: UDC is already split from CDC
call: unio_breaks

UDC broken from CDC.

- @inject_party: Back
- @post_event: Done

@dl_inject
title: Form DL
choose-if: not dl_formed and unio_split
unavailable-subtitle: DL has already been formed, or UDC has not been split yet
call: dl_formation

DL formed from CDC.

- @inject_party: Back
- @post_event: Done

@pdcat_inject
title: Form PDeCAT
choose-if: dl_formed and not pdcat_formed
unavailable-subtitle: PDeCAT has already been formed, or DL has not been formed yet
call: pdcat_formation

PDeCAT formed from CDC.

- @inject_party: Back
- @post_event: Done

